text: Hello?
Hey!
Who is this?
Hey!
Where are you right now?
Just heading back from work. It's nice and chilly out.
Ick. Chilly is seriously not cool for me
But it is cool.
Well, yes
But I don't know how you deal with it
Anyways.
Look who I met at work today
Awww
You shouldn't hold it like that...
Who is this?
Very funny. I know it's you lol
Yea, you got me.
Where are you right now?
Just heading home from work.
How was it?
Same as usual.
Could be better...
Same as usual.
Just a bit boring, really.
I'd much rather be writing for my book than for the topics they tend to focus on.
Maybe you can write an article about me lol
Haha no way
What would I even say about you?
You could tell them about the friend I made today
Awww
You shouldn't hold it like that...
Could be better...
My supervisor was on my case today about my choice of words in the piece about "Grimoire Oblique"
Apparently she wanted me to help sell the film, not expose it as the failure it is.
Well it wasn't THAT bad...
Okay maybe it was that bad
But it's the so bad it's good kind of bad
That's about the only thing it has going for it.
I haven't read the book myself, but from what I hear the fans sure aren't happy with it either.
I should move on before I write myself a third article in here-
What have you been up to?
I met a friend
Awww
You shouldn't hold it like that...
Aww
Such a cutie
I love calico cats, they look so pretty
She looks pretty spooked though
Had to catch it for the photo
It was running around behind the counter, I think it smelled the food and came in
Well, the way you're
Um
Nevermind, it's probably fine.
? Ok
So hows the new place
It's beautiful
It's a little lonely
You shouldn't hold it like that...
It was just for the photo
I thought that was how cat moms held their babies?
Only as kittens.
It's not comfortable for adult cats, especially since they're a lot heavier!
Even if it looks cute it's known to cause fear and stress
So you should avoid doing that.
Sheesh its not that big a deal lol
Guess I'll keep that in mind though
So how's the new place
It's beautiful.
It's a little lonely.
Its beautiful.
Every day I wake up it's as though I'm still in a dream.
The air feels so pure, and there's just so much more green than I'm used to.
Along with all the other lovely hues I come across on my walks.
Hmm...
Surely it's still not as beautiful as you
Oh, shush
It's a different kind of beauty
You'd understand if you could see it.
I'd like to understand
Actually, that reminds me.
Have you thought about it?
Us living together.
I have. It sounds nice.
I don't think we should yet.
It's a little lonely.
Lonely, huh
I could change that
I suppose you could...
However, it is a refreshing kind of loneliness. Feels nice to have a bit of privacy for once.
Just me out here with all the little critters that roam around free.
You don't need privacy from me
This city may be full of people but I also feel pretty lonely with you gone.
Have you thought about it yet?
Us living together.
I have. It sounds nice.
I don't think we should yet.
I have. It sounds nice.
It's also exciting that it's an actual possibility now.
But I still feel nervous about it.
Isn't it a little soon?
Not really
We've known each other for long enough.
I don't see a problem with it.
Do you?
No, of course not!
But I'm still not used to this...
Ah. Sorry, I shouldn't worry so much about it.
I've only been here for a few days but there's already so much I want to show you.
I could send pictures, but I think it might spoil the surprise!
Pictures or not, I'd do anything to see you again
Been stuck here for way too long
I won't be able to leave for a while but I promise I'll do it as soon as I can
Maybe in the meantime, you could just visit?
That way, we won't have to wait until then to see each other.
Sure
I have to go. I'll talk to you soon
Oh, okay then.
Bye!
I don't think we should yet.
You don't think?
Why don't you think, Mira?
I've given you plenty of time to do so
It's about time you gave me a clear answer
That's what I think.
Look, it's not that I don't want us to
But I'm not sure about it being so soon.
I only got here a few days ago, I still need time to settle down.
This whole thing is still new to me, too...
I thought you were serious about this
I am!
Sorry...
I shouldn't worry so much. It'll probably be fine.
Not probably, it will be
I'm not trying to sound pushy or anything you know that right
I just care about you a lot
So I want this to work out and it won't if you keep trying to avoid this
I'm not avoiding anything.
Maybe you can visit first?
Before deciding. We can see how it goes from there.
Okay.
